  "title": "星見編3章17話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（翌日から、レッスンの休憩時間を使って）\n（琴乃はさくらに歌を教え始めた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Starting the next day‚ Kotono uses the break time between lessons)\n(to teach Sakura the song.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.620156150394016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈が遺した歌。それは、グランプリ決勝のために）\n（彼女が温めていたものだった。だが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The song Mana left behind. It’s a song she’d been practicing)\n(to win the Grand Prix finals. But…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.676281070709232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 16.009614404042562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんにも\n本番まで聴かせてあげない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚\nI’m not letting you hear me sing it until the finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.05961440404257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈はその歌を聴かせてくれなかった）\n（それだけ大事にしていたんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana never sang the song for me.)\n(That’s just how important it was to her.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.65295203526815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらは、琴乃の思いに応えて全力で頑張るだろう）\n（……本当にこのままでいいんだろうか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sakura will probably practice with all her heart to live up to Kotono’s desires.)\n(I wonder if this is really the best move.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、このままだと、さくらは取り返しがつかない）\n（何かを失ってしまう……そんな気がする）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Sakura is going down a path she can’t return from.)\n(She might lose something… That’s my gut feeling.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.48024829373217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、何やってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 46.286940247603155
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 46.286940247603155
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 46.486940247603165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "本気でさくらちゃんに、私の歌を歌わせるつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you actually going to let Sakura sing my song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.220273580936485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……さくらがそれを望むならな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s what Sakura wants‚ yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.44492210426717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 54.14492208042531
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風に言われたら、本心では嫌だって思ってても\n歌うわよ。だって歌えばみんなが喜ぶんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the way Kotono asked her‚ she’ll sing it even if she secretly doesn’t want to.\nHow could she not‚ when it’ll make everyone happy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.91158874709199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、それがさくらの望みなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if that’s what Sakura wants…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.91158874709199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 65.85911715704987
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "本気でそう思っているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think that’s what she wants?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.85911715704987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……分かってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I get it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.45911710936615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 70.66195158440658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "分かってない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you don’t.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.66195158440658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 72.6619516320903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "分かってる。長瀬麻奈の再来と言われ\n麻奈と重ね見られるさくらが、今やるべきことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do. Now that she’s hailed as Mana Nagase’s second coming‚\nand everyone’s comparing her to you‚ what Sakura needs to do",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.86195163209028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 79.32861829875695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈を追いかけることじゃない\nさくら自身の歌を歌うことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is not chase after you‚ Mana.\nShe needs to sing her own song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.42861829875697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるなら、そう言いなさいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you really do get it‚ you need to tell her that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.15419632076012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 88.04417358516442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "私が歌わなくていいって、言ってるのよ！\n他ならぬ長瀬麻奈が！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell her she doesn’t need to sing my song!\nNone other than Mana Nagase herself says so!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2108402518311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それを、麻奈がテレビに出て言ってくれるなら\n誰も苦労はしない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you could go on TV and say so yourself‚\nno one would have to agonize over this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.37746158717857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 100.23501765777876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.23501765777876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 101.79762535145093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、麻奈は志半ばで亡くなったと思っている\nその麻奈と同じ声を持つ少女がグランプリに現れたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone thinks you passed away before you could achieve your dream.\nAnd now this girl with your voice showed up at the Grand Prix‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.89762535145094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "彼女が、天国の麻奈に歌声を届けてくれることを\nみんな期待している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "they all expect her song to reach you up in Heaven.\nThat’s what they’re all hoping for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.33095868478424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 117.21413326313304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、さくらちゃんにそうしろって言うの？\n結局はそっちの方が受けるからってだけじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But is that any excuse to make Sakura go through with it?\nYou’re just letting this happen because it’s good publicity!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.01413326313302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "もういい。私が芽衣ちゃんに話すから\n芽衣ちゃんからさくらちゃんに言ってもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ fine. I’ll go talk to Mei.\nI’ll get her to deliver my message to Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.88276308686201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "わ……！　待て！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Agh! Wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.38276308686207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_14_02-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "なーんてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just kidding.",
        "id": ""
      },
